have control over 3 servos and an "engine" in the servo channels
communicate with a gps to deterimne position and travel direction 
be able to path from a current location to another set location
flying in 2d coordinate based system with 30 foot range around "point"
use a wifi module with personal webpage code to upload coordinates
use wifi to know when to start


